                        <p class="unarmed-description">Detailed reporting of all security incidents, maintaining accurate logs, and providing comprehensive documentation for management.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="unarmed-card">
                        <div class="unarmed-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-route"></i>
                        </div>
